                {
                    "content": "1 In this experiment, you will investigate a light-dependent resistor (LDR).",
                    "type": "text",
                    "extra": {}
                }
            ],
            "parts": [
                {
                    "label": "a",
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "content": "(a) Connect the circuit shown in Fig. 1.1.",
