                            "extra": {}
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "image_name_placeholder",
                            "type": "image",
                            "extra": {
                                "caption": "Fig. 1.1"
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "Ensure that the switch S is open.",
                            "type": "text",
                            "extra": {}
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "Slide the LDR leads into the tube until the front of the LDR is just level with the open end of the tube, as shown in Fig. 1.1.",
                            "type": "text",
                            "extra": {}
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "With the LDR in this position, attach a piece of adhesive tape to the leads as a marker at the other end of the tube, as shown in Fig. 1.1.",
                            "type": "text",
                            "extra": {}
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "Slide the tube until the LDR is approximately half-way along it, as shown in Fig. 1.2.",
                            "type": "text",
                            "extra": {}
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "image_name_placeholder",
                            "type": "image",
                            "extra": {
                                "caption": "Fig. 1.2"
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "The distance between the tape and the tube is x.",
                            "type": "text",
                            "extra": {}
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "Measure and record x.",
                            "type": "text",
                            "extra": {}
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "x = .....................................................................",
                            "type": "text",
                            "extra": {}
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "Close S and record the ammeter reading I.",
                            "type": "text",
                            "extra": {}
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "I = .....................................................................",
                            "type": "text",
                            "extra": {}
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "Open S.",
                            "type": "text",
                            "extra": {}
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "label": "b",
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "content": "(b) Change x by moving the LDR to a new position inside the tube, with x in the range 4 cm to 18 cm. Record x and I.",
                            "type": "text",
                            "extra": {}
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "Repeat until you have six sets of values of x and I.",
                            "type": "text",
                            "extra": {}
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "Record your results in a table. Include values of √I in your table.",
                            "type": "text",
                            "extra": {}
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "label": "c",
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "content": "(c) (i) Plot a graph of √I on the y-axis against x on the x-axis.",
                            "type": "text",
                            "extra": {}
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "(ii) Draw the straight line of best fit.",
                            "type": "text",
                            "extra": {}
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "(iii) Determine the gradient and y-intercept of this line.",
                            "type": "text",
                            "extra": {}
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "gradient = ..........................................................",
                            "type": "text",
                            "extra": {}
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "y-intercept = ......................................................",
                            "type": "text",
                            "extra": {}
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "label": "d",
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "content": "(d) It is suggested that the quantities I and x are related by the equation",
                            "type": "text",
                            "extra": {}
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "√I = ax + b",
                            "type": "blockMath",
                            "extra": {}
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "where a and b are constants.",
                            "type": "text",
                            "extra": {}
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "Using your answers in (c)(iii), determine the values of a and b.",
